| AFFECT_FOR_ALL_DATABASES | tinyint(4)       | NO   |     |         |       |
| AFFECT_FOR_ALL_TABLES    | tinyint(4)       | NO   |     |         |       |
| AFFECT_DATABASE          | varchar(128)     | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| AFFECT_TABLE             | varchar(256)     | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| AFFECT_DML               | bigint(20)       | NO   |     |         |       |
| AFFECT_SCOPE             | bigint(20)       | NO   |     |         |       |
| CCL_KEYWORDS             | varchar(1048576) | NO   |     | NULL    |       |
| MAX_CONCURRENCY          | bigint(20)       | NO   |     |         |       |
